        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/06/2026-06-05-21-03-19-mozilla-central/firefox-153.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:dd5951cb294b56919c55bc3517d8c9f4da5a6f7c32caf9f90356d0cd38c5774818a5e7071347272a57910fcc7f880144ff26548cdcf5283b7df45e8f237b9dce"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/06/2026-06-05-21-03-19-mozilla-central/firefox-153.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
